This was absolutely delicious and super easy to make! I wondered about the combination of liver and blue cheese but the strong flavors were very harmonious. Didn't have brandy so I substituted bourbon and that was fine too. Leftovers make a lovely sandwich spread on crusty bread with sweet onion.....

Rating: 4
Excellent pate! We had been using an earlier recipe and at first thought this would be too rich with the blue cheese, but it was just right. I would still add a teaspoon or so of lemon zest to brighten the flavor a bit. Made it for Thanksgiving to rave reviews and made it again (a double batch) for this Christmas!